Sentencas: The crystal phase, chemical stability, thermal expansion behavior, oxygen non-stoichiometry, electrical conductivity, and electro-catalytic activity of La0.7Ca0.3Cr0.8X0.2O3-delta (X= Ti, Mn, Fe, Co, and Ni) electrode materials have been investigated.
Titulo: Investigation of aliovalent transition metal doped La0.7Ca0.3Cr0.8X0.2O3-δ (X= Ti, Mn, Fe, Co, and Ni) as electrode materials for symmetric solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: All the compositions are chemically stable with a single-phase perovskite structure in both reducing and oxidizing atmospheres at high temperature.
